Description: media player interface (MPRIS2) bridge for MPD
 mpDris2 is an implementation of the MPRIS2 media player interface as a
 client for MPD, allowing MPRIS2 clients to control MPD and observe its
 track changes via a standard D-Bus interface. The daemon runs entirely
 on asyncio: python-mpd2 for the MPD protocol and dbus-fast for the
 MPRIS interface.
 .
 The package ships a user systemd unit (not auto-enabled).
